nk?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1anlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=4c542a26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">除咗九月八日，如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月一日</span>我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？<br />\n<br />\n而最重要，我地之前揮動美國國旗、唱美國國歌，美國傳媒一直都理解成我地係以追求人權民主自由既普世價值而表態！！！亦係動之以情地令佢地推動 香港人權及民主法案 既方法！！！<br />\n</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n九月八日發夢同我一齊唱！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1anlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=54cf461b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSVsMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nSVsMz.png&h=279e88f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Make Hong Kong great again!</span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e8e20dab39ff467cbebd007952ad3d7bc1ce8929","tid":1532130,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"英文2咗係冇可能Yr 1走，即使補IELTS都好難走，因為中六畢業入大學要有3322係政府規定嘅入學最基本要求，而點解Asso上大學可以有3322係因為你已經讀完Asso，資歷架構上會升咗一級，於是唔再需要跟上述呢個要求。點解話幾乎冇可能走呢，係因為大學要收一個冇3322嘅Asso yr1學生係要寫信俾政府解釋，大學唔會特登為你做啲咁嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n俾心機專心谷爆yr 1嘅GPA、操IELTS（建議谷Listening），以yr 2入三大為目標！加油呀！"},{"pid":"488dcbc099ecf56da64415ed6ebcb0fd303d20a5","tid":1532130,"uid":198497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:53:33.000Z","msg":"year1升u其實好睇dse成績<br />\n同埋你入到u係year1, 變相讀多年，當然，你可以享受返u life<br />\n<br />\nyear2升大學多數上大學year3<br />\n<br />\n而gpa係accumulate既，所以你year 1一定要爆gpa, gpa係interview既門檻，non ju Interview先佔最重<br />\n<br />\nbtw你year2先報大學既話千萬唔好報year1, 一定要報year3, 因為你asso year2報 大學year1多數睇都唔睇(我直接係入學處同professor到聽返黎)<br />\n<br />\n利申asso year2 上返ugc year3"}]}